      "created_at": "2022-08-05T20:29:26.407Z",
      "updated_at": "2022-08-05T20:29:26.407Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Archives are up on YouTube <img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/twitter/partying_face.png?v=12\" title=\":partying_face:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":partying_face:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"><img src=\"https://emoji.discourse-cdn.com/twitter/vulcan_salute.png?v=12\" title=\":vulcan_salute:\" class=\"emoji\" alt=\":vulcan_salute:\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"20\" height=\"20\"></p><div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"mkPGcwb9ezg\" data-video-title=\"Dr. Rek - Ambient Mafia 07-24-22 - Live AV set\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=mkPGcwb9ezg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/d/dcd0b0b0dbe92401ec225759e6485ecc9d59c8d6.jpeg\" title=\"Dr. Rek - Ambient Mafia 07-24-22 - Live AV set\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n<div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"BNIImquR7yo\" data-video-title=\"Rek'n It 003 - RELMS\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=BNIImquR7yo\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/e/e023e38e6829e4a3f1203e6510c4444c6ae2c880.jpeg\" title=\"Rek'n It 003 - RELMS\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n",
