      "updated_at": "2022-09-14T17:25:10.490Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Playlist for a full day of entertainments<br>\n            <iframe src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/mkPGcwb9ezg?feature=oembed&amp;wmode=opaque&amp;list=PLjhmkr3Zmjur5taxSGfMEmkgokDY58Mc6\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\" frameborder=\"0\" allowfullscreen=\"\" class=\"youtube-onebox\" seamless=\"seamless\" sandbox=\"allow-same-origin allow-scripts allow-forms allow-popups allow-popups-to-escape-sandbox allow-presentation\"></iframe>\n</p>",
