      "post_number": 9,
      "username": "Dr_Rek",
      "name": "Derek Sajbel",
      "created_at": "2022-09-21T21:31:07.493Z",
      "updated_at": "2022-09-21T21:31:07.493Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Did visuals for DJ CZ at Chillits last weekend. My personal AV set from Chillits post coming next week. Both sets feature DSG3 and other Gen3 modules throughout. Very happy with the DSG3 and Mapper combo, infinite rainbow shapes!</p><div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"xv908_3jLPQ\" data-video-title=\"Chillits 2022 - DJ CZ with Dr. Rek visuals\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xv908_3jLPQ\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/a/a0da764711b424e9f31ba652f2578322ad608254.jpeg\" title=\"Chillits 2022 - DJ CZ with Dr. Rek visuals\" width=\"480\" height=\"360\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n",
      "like_count": 0,
      "reply_to_post_number": null,
      "is_wiki": false
    },
    {
      "id": 28893,
      "post_number": 10,
      "username": "Z0NK0UT",
      "name": "Chad @ LZX Industries",
      "created_at": "2022-09-22T16:15:25.521Z",
      "updated_at": "2022-09-22T16:15:25.521Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Looking good! Nice to see DSG3 and MemPal hanging out with the AI Furbies.</p>",
      "like_count": 0,
      "reply_to_post_number": 9,
      "is_wiki": false
