    {
      "id": 28981,
      "post_number": 11,
      "username": "Dr_Rek",
      "name": "Derek Sajbel",
      "created_at": "2022-09-29T18:57:50.362Z",
      "updated_at": "2022-09-29T18:58:31.464Z",
      "cooked": "<p>Lots of DSG3 Mapper rainbows in my set from Chillits, I used a less complex patch with Sensory Translator, Baja and Pendulum mixed in Submixer into DSG3 &gt; Mapper &gt; ESG3 to focus on rainbows for this Friday Night performance the night before the above CZ set.</p><div class=\"youtube-onebox lazy-video-container\" data-video-id=\"ipOs_aE3aOU\" data-video-title=\"Chillits 2022 - Dr. Rek Audio Visual mix\" data-provider-name=\"youtube\">\n  <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ipOs_aE3aOU\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener nofollow ugc\">\n    <img class=\"youtube-thumbnail\" src=\"https://canada1.discourse-cdn.com/flex031/uploads/lzxindustries/original/2X/4/4ffdef55ae1c51ee1113cf48eb2d30755578fdd4.jpeg\" title=\"Chillits 2022 - Dr. Rek Audio Visual mix\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\">\n  </a>\n</div>\n",
      "like_count": 0,
      "reply_to_post_number": 10,
      "is_wiki": false
    },
